email.voterEmail:
Thanks for sending in your FPCA form to your local election office. Here is a copy for your records. 

**Please note this is an automated email from Vote From Abroad and not confirmation of receipt from your local election office.**

Be sure to contact your local election office to verify they received your form. Only your election office can process your form and send out your ballot. Email or call your election office to ensure you will receive your ballot: 

 {leoName} 

 Email: {leoEmail} 

 Phone: {leoPhone} 

 If you need any help, contact our volunteer voter support team at help@votefromabroad.org. 

